Rating: 4
I first made this as an appetizer for a casual dinner with friends. Since part of our group did not eat meat I took out the prosciutto. This would normally leave a very boring antipasto salad, but not in this case. The dressing is so flavorful and eggs add such an unusual balance that this has become my favorite do ahead, easy party dishes.

